channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Tennessee Volunteers’ New “Smokey Grey” Alternate Jerseys Leak
item.description: For the second year in a row, Tennessee had its new “Smokey Grey” alternate jersey leaked by Dick’s Sporting Goods after the retailer had a mannequin wearing the jersey on display on Friday afternoon.

item.title: Washington Wizards Unveil 2024-25 Statement Edition Uniforms
item.description: The Washington Wizards unveiled their 2024-25 Statement Edition uniforms early Friday morning, replacing the set they've worn since the 2019-20 season.
